{"tid":506061,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"老狗亂痾屎，點解決？","createTime":"2017-12-21T21:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T02:28:57.000Z","uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ab528a482baf9615bb84601facbbcd5ede4f8bee","tid":506061,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T21:42:54.000Z","msg":"最近寄人籬下，屋主有幾隻狗，由細養大。<br />\n我就唔驚狗既，佢工人又會日日上門清潔，但問題係：每晚返到屋都會周地屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我留意左好耐，係其中一隻老狗特別鐘意隨地解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獲獲喂完佢食狗餅佢就即痾，完全冇去屎盤個衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他老狗就好唔同，識自己去盤到痾屎痾尿，係隻仆街白狗麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時痾到成個廚房都係，我對狗冇抗拒但對屎有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點訓練佢？"},{"pid":"7f50f62322e69422c9f291b49b5d8f97c86ed047","tid":506061,"uid":142707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T21:44:08.000Z","msg":"比屎佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3eb1dc668253fd6bc8b7189f7f746cc84c367f","tid":506061,"uid":142433,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T21:48:43.000Z","msg":"訓你老母練 你都識講老狗<br />\n寄人籬下就咪撚咁多野講"},{"pid":"b45c3ea7b464b19c15b189cd3526da715072815e","tid":506061,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T22:47:47.000Z","msg":"老狗可能係因為身體有問題，已經做唔到<br />\n你話其他狗都識去廁所，咁佢地既主人應該無理由全部都訓練，唯獨就唔教依一隻掛？"},{"pid":"694d1c1863ed91fd1edc01d051c1f5302c29e0c5","tid":506061,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T23:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比屎佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有用<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係唔係直接食<br />\n<br />\n擺舊屎係佢休息地方<br />\n或者將佢休息個地方，如狗窩<br />\n放近佢屙屎個位"},{"pid":"bb7be8e2eccf742cf15c99d5a2a5330ea346ab63","tid":506061,"uid":71425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T23:12:04.000Z","msg":"屋主都未出聲，關你鳩事"},{"pid":"f9a8fd6101a6cc7d9a3ae29dbb70b8a52ea37290","tid":506061,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T23:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比屎佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有用<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係唔係直接食<br />\n<br />\n擺舊屎係佢休息地方<br />\n或者將佢休息個地方，如狗窩<br />\n放近佢屙屎個位</blockquote><br />\n真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你咁做同佢講係休息既地方都可以屙屎無分別，佢地唔係人類唔會覺得咁係整蠱佢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0430c6d5974703428ac67011f4c018fe897d2e56","tid":506061,"uid":106930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近寄人籬下，屋主有幾隻狗，由細養大。<br />\n我就唔驚狗既，佢工人又會日日上門清潔，但問題係：每晚返到屋都會周地屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我留意左好耐，係其中一隻老狗特別鐘意隨地解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獲獲喂完佢食狗餅佢就即痾，完全冇去屎盤個衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他老狗就好唔同，識自己去盤到痾屎痾尿，係隻仆街白狗麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時痾到成個廚房都係，我對狗冇抗拒但對屎有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點訓練佢？</blockquote><br />\n你有無諗過隻老狗都會有身體機能退化既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲train 乜9？"},{"pid":"0f94aa6123c7d2bcaad009824841f29d8aea0831","tid":506061,"uid":45684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"你食咗舊屎, 舊屎咪唔再存在"},{"pid":"b46ed2e7a9ebd9c697f93578c204b267157978b7","tid":506061,"uid":706,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T03:45:03.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩死乞衣<br />\n乞人地方住仲咁撚多野講<br />\n你咁撚廢第一件事要解決既就係你自己啦"},{"pid":"a5b044f08caffc50711dd6bb85f05144db060fe7","tid":506061,"uid":25463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"身體機能退化佢未必想既<br />\n如果佢食完就會想柯不如佢一食完你就帶佢去廁所啦"},{"pid":"014e789990fbcebb4cec7cbf0baf3dcf82c09c12","tid":506061,"uid":146856,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T13:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近寄人籬下，屋主有幾隻狗，由細養大。<br />\n我就唔驚狗既，佢工人又會日日上門清潔，但問題係：每晚返到屋都會周地屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我留意左好耐，係其中一隻老狗特別鐘意隨地解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獲獲喂完佢食狗餅佢就即痾，完全冇去屎盤個衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他老狗就好唔同，識自己去盤到痾屎痾尿，係隻仆街白狗麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時痾到成個廚房都係，我對狗冇抗拒但對屎有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點訓練佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個問題唔係隻狗度 而係你自己<br />\n強烈建議將你自已同帶埋自己啲垃圾掟晒出門口就解決問題<br />\n<br />\n食撚屎啦 寄人籬下仲咁撚多嗲 <br />\n你老豆老母老咗都可能有呢個問題<br />\n你到時候又諗住上嚟問點train佢哋？"},{"pid":"559e1dfb1a4b8cab3fae1e23133be1fbdd0e18ca","tid":506061,"uid":29942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"you can't teach an old dog new tricks"},{"pid":"fc1f4ac397989321195ea60b42eaf56b8ba8916b","tid":506061,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T19:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我都有比租既"},{"pid":"3b6d6bba0d859fc0d71cf61e8c0c7d4f4b09a2d9","tid":506061,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T22:50:22.000Z","msg":"老狗身體機能退化，佢都唔想的！"},{"p